metadata.name: 🏝 ISLAND OF THE FROG 🐸
metadata.description:
Island that seems desolate but really
below is a cave full of mineral “Ethereum” there is a octopus guarding of entrance
Under water there are many sea creatures that can be friends of frogs
So frog built a cottage on this island and come back to stay every time come to the sea.
